      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FOOLS RUSH IN (5) has been in the money at her last two runs, most recently when third beaten 6 lengths (30.93). Goes well here including a win and six minors. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Expected to feature in the finish again. OXLEY FLYER (2) goes very well over this track and trip including two wins. Below best last time at this track (18.23) in a Grade 4, finishing a 10 length seventh. Can hit the frame with the right run. ZIPPING LYNDY (7) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth (30.96) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Solid record at the distance winning two races. Should be thereabouts. FLYING GODDESS (8) is another with top-three prospects.",
